videos.description: Isaiah Wilkins scores a layup off a nice feed from Jack Salt and gets fouled in the process for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Virginia's Wilkins goes up strong for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Jack Salt threads the needle to Isaiah Wilkins, who sends home a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Virginia's Wilkins throws down two-handed dunk

videos.description: Devon Hall erupts the crowd with a powerful dunk off a beautiful feed from Nigel Johnson.
videos.headline: Virginia turns tenacious defense into easy fast-break bucket

videos.description: Nigel Johnson lobs a pass to Mamadi Diakite for a strong alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Virginia's Diakite soars for alley-oop

videos.description: Nigel Johnson feeds Jay Huff in transition for an easy dunk and foul.
videos.headline: Virginia's Huff slams a dunk for 3-point play

videos.description: No. 18 Virginia improves to 8-0 with a 75-54 win over Lehigh.
videos.headline: Virginia cruises to remain undefeated
